descriptionHtml: Inspired by the legendary Los Angeles skateboard spot, the Belmont is a skate take on a classic apron front derby. A two-tone upper in combinations of velvet, exotic patterned calf hair, and box calf leathers is expertly stitched on a classic Margom court outsole. Woven, waxed, gold-tipped laces tie it all together with a louche elegance.
